channel.title: Help with Running
channel.description:
I need help with the "run server.bat" I keep getting
starting... [Launcher] Loading ExtremeKO, please wait... Exception in thread "main" java.io.FileNotFoundException: data\cache\main_file_c ache.dat2 (Access is denied) at java.io.RandomAccessFile.open(Native Method) at java.io.RandomAccessFile.<init>(RandomAccessFile.java:236) at java.io.RandomAccessFile.<init>(RandomAccessFile.java:118) at com.alex.store.Store.<init>(Store.java:25) at com.alex.store.Store.<init>(Store.java:19) at com.rs.cache.Cache.init(Cache.java:22) at com.rs.Initializer.loadFiles(Initializer.java:39) at com.rs.Launcher.main(Launcher.java:42) Press any key to continue . . .
I have tried everything in my power to fix it, I have looked up stuff and nothing has helped >.< this is my last resort. So if you could help it would be much thanked!!! Also i am showing my code academy some of the changes I have made to the server :P it's due Friday please help!
